-𝐑𝐞𝐪𝐮𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬-
1️⃣Follow @theskiing + @snow_sends 
2️⃣Tag 2 Friends (Every additional is 1+ entry)
3️⃣ Message “DONE” to: @theskiing
4️⃣ EXTRA POINTS: Repost giveaway to story
—————————————————————
Shipping fees apply because of weight, and location.
